ry-plans-on-pause&quot;>;今年早些时候搁置了乔治亚州工厂的计划&lt;/a>;。这次暂停也让 Rivian 能够更快地推出中型 R2 车辆。自 2021 年 11 月公开发行以来，该公司已经损失了大量资金，其中上一季度损失了 11 亿美元。该公司最近表示，预计今年调整后收益将损失高达 28.8 亿美元，高于之前指导的 27 亿美元损失。它已经&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/2/21/24079572/rivian-layoff-ev-production-q4-earnings&quot;>;通过&lt;/a>; &lt;a href=&quot; https://www.theverge.com/2023/2/1/23581642/rivian-layoff-ev-workers-employees-price-cut&quot;>;几个&lt;/a>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2022/7/11/23204199/rivian-electric-vehicles-layoffs-planned-manufacturing&quot;>;过去的几轮裁员&lt;/a>;...&lt; /p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/26/24306402/rivian-doe-atvm-loan-georgia-ev-factory-trump&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/26/24306402/rivian-doe-atvm-loan-georgia-ev-factory-trump" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/26/24306402/rivian-doe-atvm-loan-georgia-ev-factory-trump</id><author><name>安德鲁·霍金斯</name></author></entry></feed>